    <title>vibecoding项目迭代</title>
    <url>/2026/04/08/vibecoding%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%BF%AD%E4%BB%A3/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><p>上创业课太无聊了，我居然点进了哔站刷视频，于是乎就看到这么个视频【小白AI编程进阶：不写一行代码，教你Vibecoding项目完美升级！】<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV16CXTBDEAc?vd_source=2d766142e23921a5dff311236709cd7e%E3%80%82%E5%94%89%EF%BC%8Cvibecoding%E7%9A%84%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E8%B7%9F%E4%B8%8A%E5%8E%BB%E5%AD%A6%E4%B8%80%E5%AD%A6%EF%BC%8C%E8%B7%AF%E8%BE%B9%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E7%88%B7%E5%BE%85%E4%BC%9A%E9%83%BD%E6%AF%94%E6%88%91%E6%9B%B4%E4%BC%9A%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E4%BA%86%E3%80%82">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV16CXTBDEAc?vd_source=2d766142e23921a5dff311236709cd7e。唉，vibecoding的时代，不跟上去学一学，路边的大爷待会都比我更会编程了。</a></p>
<p>我将把这个视频所传知识化为己有。</p>
<p>懒得仔细看就直接看最后的总结图片。</p>
<h1 id="小改"><a href="#小改" class="headerlink" title="小改"></a>小改</h1><p><img   lazyload src="/assets/images/Meow-Loading.webp" data-lazy-src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Hafsun/blogs_pic/main/images20260408210329014.png"  alt="image-20260408210328987"></p>
<p>如上图，直接截图告诉它就行，改完后看效果，不满意再改。</p>
<h1 id="大改"><a href="#大改" class="headerlink" title="大改"></a>大改</h1><h3 id="1、存档"><a href="#1、存档" class="headerlink" title="1、存档"></a>1、存档</h3><p><img   lazyload src="/assets/images/Meow-Loading.webp" data-lazy-src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Hafsun/blogs_pic/main/images20260408210349026.png"  alt="image-20260408210348995"></p>
<p>用如上图的方式让AI帮打包，或者用github进行版本管理。</p>
<h3 id="2、写迭代文档PRD"><a href="#2、写迭代文档PRD" class="headerlink" title="2、写迭代文档PRD"></a>2、写迭代文档PRD</h3><p>找到一个厉害点的大模型，告诉它：</p>
<p><img   lazyload src="/assets/images/Meow-Loading.webp" data-lazy-src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Hafsun/blogs_pic/main/images20260408210410691.png"  alt="image-20260408210410652"></p>
<p>如果有不满意的地方，截图丢回去让它改，如下图</p>
<p><img   lazyload src="/assets/images/Meow-Loading.webp" data-lazy-src="https://gitee.com/han-fangfang/blogs_picture/raw/master/20260408201828383.png"  alt="image-20260408201828348"></p>
<p>最终，我们应该得到了一份满意的迭代PRD</p>
<h3 id="3、IDE内行动"><a href="#3、IDE内行动" class="headerlink" title="3、IDE内行动"></a>3、IDE内行动</h3><p><img   lazyload src="/assets/images/Meow-Loading.webp" data-lazy-src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Hafsun/blogs_pic/main/images20260408210458951.png"  alt="image-20260408210458859"></p>
<p><img   lazyload src="/assets/images/Meow-Loading.webp" data-lazy-src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Hafsun/blogs_pic/main/images20260408210512601.png"  alt="image-20260408210512578"></p>
<p>建立这样的文件结构，前面大模型给的迭代prd和迭代html代码就放在迭代2.0这样的目录下。</p>
<p>然后把迭代2.0目录右击，添加到对话，就像这样：</p>
<p><img   lazyload src="/assets/images/Meow-Loading.webp" data-lazy-src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Hafsun/blogs_pic/main/images20260408210539600.png"  alt="image-20260408210539578"></p>
<p>然后切换到plan模式，并：</p>
<p><img   lazyload src="/assets/images/Meow-Loading.webp" data-lazy-src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Hafsun/blogs_pic/main/images20260408210552887.png"  alt="image-20260408210552859"></p>
<p>完了之后点击计划给出的build按钮，也就是开始编码</p>
<h3 id="4、备忘"><a href="#4、备忘" class="headerlink" title="4、备忘"></a>4、备忘</h3><p><img   lazyload src="/assets/images/Meow-Loading.webp" data-lazy-src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Hafsun/blogs_pic/main/images20260408210601648.png"  alt="image-20260408210601618"></p>
<p>也就是总结一下这次迭代都干了些啥</p>
<h1 id="总结图片"><a href="#总结图片" class="headerlink" title="总结图片"></a>总结图片</h1><p><img   lazyload src="/assets/images/Meow-Loading.webp" data-lazy-src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Hafsun/blogs_pic/main/images20260408210611798.png"  alt="image-20260408210611675"></p>
]]></content>
